        <body>       
                <pb n="1"/>
            <p>26.1.85<lb/></p>
            <p>Rev S Morais<lb/>
                My dear Sir<lb/></p>
            <p>I am very sorry you<lb/> cannot come this week. Can you<lb/> next or even the week after&#63;<lb/></p>
            <p>Your presence would<lb/> draw a proper audience&#59; my speaking<lb/> without you would draw only my<lb/> usual audience&#44; not the folks I want.<lb/> You will&#44; on the other hand&#44; draw that<lb/> very class.<lb/></p>
            <p>Moreover I thought that reading my<lb/> paper on Congregational Work would have<lb/> better results with a larger audience.<lb/> Hence by coming you will do a double<lb/> Mitzva. You will forward the Alliance<lb/> &#40;setting the example for other Congregations to<lb/> follow&#41; and you will give me an opportunity<lb/> to stir up the comatose people a little&#44;<lb/> Please try and reconsider&#44;&#45;&#45; I will come<lb/></p>
                
                <pb n="2"/>
            <p>specially to escort you as our congregation&#39;s <lb/> guest.<lb/></p>
            <p>Hoping to hear favorably<lb/>
                Yrs<lb/>
                H Pereira Mendes.<lb/></p>
        </body>
    </text>
